ActSechelt Indian Band Self-Government Act
SubjectFinancial Transfer Agreements with the Sechelt Indian Band
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Indian Affairs and Northern Development to enter into renewed FINANCIAL TRANSFER AGREEMENTS with the Sechelt Indian Band in order to support Self-Governing Indigenous Governments in continuing to deliver programs and services to their citizens and implement their respective modern treaty and/or self-government arrangements.
